dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents land use for Monroe County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Monroe_LandUse_YE2016.gdb'.[Prepared in 2010 from aerial imagery and other available data for the Monroe County Comprehensive Plan document. The Monroe County Comprehensive Plan was prepared by Crispell-Snyder, Inc. under the direction of the Monroe County Zoning Committee.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
